snippet.textDisplay: For those of you who didn't know, Imagine Dragons never intended to release a music video for Nothing Left To Say. It was originally Patrick Foch (Director) who asked ID's permission to use the song for their art film. Imagine Dragons love it so much that they asked Patrick to release it on their YouTube channel instead.
